<A>__{there is a gentle knock at the door, and mr. peters enters. he carries a tray of coffee. he keeps his eyes modestly lowered.}
<C>__{mr. peters}
<D>__{on the house.}
<A>__{he lays the tray on a table, still keeping his eyes lowered, and goes out.}
<C>__{milly}
<D>__{some house! hope it falls on his ruddy earhole!}
